{"tid":280454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台會在未來數小時考慮改發八號烈風或暴風信號。","createTime":"2017-06-12T05:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T18:18:31.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d1f0c28d7d20af47d8e61f87bd874b78e70b4d27","tid":280454,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/content_elements_v2/images/tc_track/tctrack_1707_uc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fcontent_elements_v2%2Fimages%2Ftc_track%2Ftctrack_1707_uc.png&h=c42b086e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n按照現時預測路徑，苗柏約在今晚午夜時份在香港一百公里範圍內登陸。雖然與苗柏相關的烈風範圍較小，並主要集中在其中心東面及南面，但由於苗柏會在今日稍後相當接近香港，本港特別是東部地區仍有機會受其烈風影響。<br />\n<br />\n天文台會在未來數小時考慮改發八號烈風或暴風信號。<br />\n<br />\n海面有大浪及湧浪，市民應遠離岸邊及停止所有水上活動。<br />\n<br />\n在過去一小時，橫瀾島及西貢分別錄得的最高持續風速為每小時67及42公里。"},{"pid":"d6fdd44f97b8b7c4be6a34aeccff9ab0290dfe2e","tid":280454,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:51:10.000Z","msg":"汁野收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80eac1d837ff96a3bd5a1b0eb2df29574761bbba","tid":280454,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:51:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"654990f3ea6bf310aa21756c60cb65753e6324c3","tid":280454,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:52:07.000Z","msg":"汁野收工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069e3b2420c665a4c5a493d03e5e4be48cf0c2f2","tid":280454,"uid":2936,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>汁野收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n汁你老味咩 汁<img